'''Clan Secura''' or '''House Secura''' was a famous and influential [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] family on [[Ryloth/Legends|Ryloth]]. Among its members were [[Lon Secura]], [[Pol Secura]], [[Nat Secura]], [[Van Secura]], and [[Aayla Secura/Legends|Aayla Secura]]. "Secura" meant "skilled" in [[Twi'leki/Legends|Ryl]].

